      "_dirType": "sub",
      "0": {
        "_dirName": "0",
        "_dirType": "String",
        "_value": "Oh, thanks for coming! I just got a new request in store for you. This time, it's #b#p414##k, the assistant from the beauty parlor. #b#p414##k is actually a lonely guy living by himself. He's apparently sick and tired of eating the same old junk."
      },
      "1": {
        "_dirName": "1",
        "_dirType": "String",
        "_value": "Well, I can whip up some delicious Seafood Soup using #b20 #t4000012#s#k and #b1 #t2022000##k. That should be easy enough, right? Come see me after you've defeated #b30 #o12#es#k and collected everything. I'll be waiting!"
      }
    },
    "1": {
      "_dirName": "1",
      "_dirType": "sub",
      "0": {
        "_dirName": "0",
        "_dirType": "String",
        "_value": "I knew I could count on you. Since you've done such a wonderful job following through with the request, here's your reward. #b#p414##k is giving you a glove that'll help you on your journey, so go ahead and take it!"
      },
      "yes": {
        "_dirName": "yes",
        "_dirType": "sub",
        "0": {
          "_dirName": "0",
          "_dirType": "String",
          "_value": "Alright, if you need work sometime down the road, feel free to come back and see me."
        }
      },
